title: Ashampoo Snap 2017 GOTD
description:
Ashampoo Snap 2017 GOTD

With Ashampoo Snap 2017, you can get screen captures and even videos and easily edit them.

Create sequence of images and by combining multiple screenshots, it supports resolutions up to 4K.

Resize them automatically and apply other editing functions to videos

Main Features:
Easy to navigate and use
Easy to use with the 1-click button
Save all your snapshots and select which format you want
Quickly edit and manage
Supports 4k and high resolutions
Different visual tools available

Official Website: https://www.ashampoo.com/en/usd/pin/1824/multimedia-software/Ashampoo-Snap-2017
